      "title": "🌴 Back End - Intermediate developer for live video startup @ Mastermind",
      "description": "<p><strong>Mastermind</strong> is a tech startup that helps anyone <strong>build a paid community using live video</strong>.  Our platform is designed to help launch a single event, a course or an entire branded community.  Our founders (<a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/chrissukornyk/?originalSubdomain=ca\">Chris</a> &amp; <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/candicefaktor/\">Candice</a>) are seasoned tech entrepreneurs with several successful exits to their credit.  You will be working directly with the founders on a small (entirely remote) team rapidly iterating towards our product-market fit.  We hire for character, team fit AND skills.</p>\n<p><strong>Make something people want</strong></p>\n<p>We've done extensive customer interviews and have an MVP under development and in the hands of a small customer council.  We're well funded, with many well known angel investors participating and now we have the opportunity to build an incredible product that solves real problems.</p>\n<p><strong>Create a huge impact</strong></p>\n<p>We're not just another software platform - this is a solution that allows entrepreneurs and next-generation teachers to fulfill their dream of sharing their passion while building a business.  This pandemic has fundamentally shifted how we learn, work and live and we want to make online learning fun and collaborative for the planet.</p>\n<p><strong>About the Role</strong></p>\n<p>As an intermediate python developer you will be working on the main platform and all RESTful Api's used by our application.  Your primary focus will be on developing backend systems with API's using Django REST framework.  You will ensure that these components and the overall application are robust and easy to maintain. You will work on a small technology team (&lt;10) with direct access to the founding team. Therefore, a commitment to collaborative problem solving, sophisticated design, and quality product is important.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Develop API's using Django</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Build reusable components</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Contribute to new features ideas and implementation</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Think like our customers - take ownership and pride in our product</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Skills</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>STRONG proficiency in Python.  5+ Years experience in Python</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Experience with Django REST framework</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Excellent communicator and fluent in English</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Strong knowledge of API architecture and experience building APIs</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Previous experience with working remotely and on startups</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Strong team player with passion for learning</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>BONUS : Any experience working with streaming video or video conferencing</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We are hiring within the next 2 weeks for this position.  This is a 100% remote job.</p>\n<p>Email <a href=\"mailto:chris@mastermind.co\">chris@mastermind.co</a></p>\n",
      "how_to_apply": "<p>Email your resume, example code to <a href=\"mailto:chris@mastermind.co\">chris@mastermind.co</a></p>\n",
      "company_logo": "https://jobs.github.com/rails/active_storage/blobs/eyJfcmFpbHMiOnsibWVzc2FnZSI6IkJBaHBBbEdMIiwiZXhwIjpudWxsLCJwdXIiOiJibG9iX2lkIn19--7ed4d248ae2bf4c5293e18a46fa8ae9765aafe01/logo2.jpg"
