      "description": "<p>We are Business Talent Group, a company that connects independent professionals with business and technical backgrounds to project-based work for our clients- both remote and onsite. We have served nearly 50% of the Fortune 100.</p>\n<p>We are launching a new large relationship with a F200 global client that expects to have numerous project needs with projects ranging from 6 weeks to 12+ months. We are looking for independent consultants/contractors/freelancers with knowledge of technical and business skills. Project managers and backgrounds in any software lifecycle development a plus. Technology segments of interest include:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Data visualization</li>\n<li>Digital supply chain</li>\n<li>CRM</li>\n<li>Data science</li>\n<li>RPA</li>\n<li>ERP &amp; Finance</li>\n<li>HR &amp; people software</li>\n<li>Procure to pay (P2P)</li>\n<li>Collaboration tools</li>\n<li>Process flow software</li>\n<li>Healthcare IT systems</li>\n<li>Database management</li>\n<li>Cloud development</li>\n</ul>\n<p>1-10+ years of experience in specific technologies is preferred. Combination of business or project management and technical expertise is a plus.</p>\n<p>If you are interested and have such backgrounds, we would be delighted to have you join our talent network. Please note, there is no cost and no commitment involved. The only investment on your end is the 15 minutes it takes to complete your registration.</p>\n<p>Being a part of our network is simply another way for you to source and apply for projects. In your profile, you will be able to code for preferred preferences such as daily rate and location. Additionally, you may apply to some of our project postings through our talent portal.</p>\n<p>Please note: in order to join our network and be considered for projects, you certify that you are not employed in a permanent role. This does not include full-time contract roles or ownership of your own independent consulting practice.</p>\n",
      "how_to_apply": "<p>Please apply directly to join our talent network using this link:\n<a href=\"http://btg.force.com/consultant/apex/ts2__jobdetails?jobId=a0o1W000007GXWm&amp;tSource=a131W00000D0UHCQA3\">http://btg.force.com/consultant/apex/ts2__jobdetails?jobId=a0o1W000007GXWm&amp;tSource=a131W00000D0UHCQA3</a></p>\n<p>Once you've applied, send a confirmation email to <a href=\"mailto:ray.paez@businesstalentgroup.com\">ray.paez@businesstalentgroup.com</a> and mention GitHub.</p>\n",
